1.5 text-xs rounded-lg border transition-colors bg-[#151515] text-[#A1A1AA] border-[#2A2A2A] hover:border-[#D4A843]\">Bio Capacity</button></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 bg-[#151515] rounded-lg border border-[#2A2A2A] p-0.5 mb-6 w-fit\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors bg-[#D4A843] text-[#0A0A0A]\">Chart</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors text-[#A1A1AA] hover:text-[#F5F5F5]\">Table</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-md transition-colors text-[#A1A1AA] hover:text-[#F5F5F5]\">Raw Data</button></div><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"border-b border-[#2A2A2A] pb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><span class=\"inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full\" style=\"background-color:#F97316\"></span><span class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#A1A1AA]\">energy</span><span class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]\">·</span><span class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]\">annual</span></div><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#F5F5F5] mb-4\">India Renewable Energy Capacity</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-[#A1A1AA] max-w-3xl\">Installed renewable energy capacity in India by source (solar, wind, hydro, bio).</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 p-4 bg-[#151515] rounded-lg border border-[#2A2A2A]\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-wider\">Source</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#F5F5F5] mt-1\">Ministry of New and Renewable Energy</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-wider\">Unit</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#F5F5F5] mt-1\">Gigawatts (GW)</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-wider\">Version</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#F5F5F5] mt-1\">1.0</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-wider\">Published</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#F5F5F5] mt-1\">1/5/2026</p></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#F5F5F5] mb-3\">Methodology</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]\">Data compiled from monthly reports of renewable energy installations. Capacity in GW at end of financial year.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Metrics</h2><div class=\"flex gap-2 flex-wrap\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-lg border transition-colors bg-[#D4A843] text-[#0A0A0A] border-[#D4A843]\">Solar Capacity<span class=\"ml-2 text-xs opacity-60\">●</span></button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-lg border transition-colors bg-[#151515] text-[#A1A1AA] border-[#2A2A2A] hover:border-[#D4A843]\">Wind Capacity</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-lg border transition-colors bg-[#151515] text-[#A1A1AA] border-[#2A2A2A] hover:border-[#D4A843]\">Hydro Capacity</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-lg border transition-colors bg-[#151515] text-[#A1A1AA] border-[#2A2A2A] hover:border-[#D4A843]\">Bio Capacity</button></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#F5F5F5] mb-1\">Solar Capacity</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] mb-4\">Total installed solar power capacity.</p><div class=\"mb-4 flex gap-2 flex-wrap\"><button class=\"px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md border transition-colors bg-[#D4A843] text-[#0A0A0A] border-[#D4A843]\">Renewable Capacity Trend by Source</button><button class=\"px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md border transition-colors bg-[#151515] text-[#A1A1AA] border-[#2A2A2A] hover:border-[#D4A843]\">Renewable Mix (2025)</button></div><div class=\"bg-[#151515] rounded-lg border border-[#2A2A2A] p-4\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 600 300\" class=\"w-full h-auto\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Renewable Capacity Trend by Source\"><text x=\"300\" y=\"16\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#A1A1AA\" font-size=\"12\">Renewable Capacity Trend by Source</text><clipPath id=\"plot-clip\"><rect x=\"60\" y=\"20\" width=\"520\" height=\"240\"></rect></clipPath><path d=\"M60.0,240.0 L164.0,194.0 L268.0,150.7 L372.0,110.4 L476.0,84.8 L580.0,40.0 L580.0,260 L60.0,260 Z\" fill=\"#D4A843\" fill-opacity=\"0.1\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></path><path d=\"M60.0,240.0 L164.0,194.0 L268.0,150.7 L372.0,110.4 L476.0,84.8 L580.0,40.0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#D4A843\" stroke-width=\"2\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></path><circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"240\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle><circle cx=\"164\" cy=\"193.96341463414635\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle><circle cx=\"268\" cy=\"150.67073170731706\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle><circle cx=\"372\" cy=\"110.42682926829272\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle><circle cx=\"476\" cy=\"84.81707317073173\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle><circle cx=\"580\" cy=\"40\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#D4A843\" clip-path=\"url(#plot-clip)\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"mt-6 bg-[#151515] rounded-lg border border-[#2A2A2A] overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-4 py-3 border-b border-[#2A2A2A]\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-[#F5F5F5]\">Data Table</h3></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-[#2A2A2A]\"><th class=\"text-left py-3 px-4 text-[#A1A1AA] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-xs\">Period</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 px-4 text-[#A1A1AA] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-xs\">Solar Capacity</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 px-4 text-[#A1A1AA] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-xs\">Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-[#2A2A2A]/50 hover:bg-[#151515] transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 px-4 text-[#F5F5F5] font-mono\">2020</td><td class=\"py-3 px-4 text-[#22C55E] font-mono\">34.6</td><td class=\"py-3 px-4 text-[#A1A1AA] text-xs\"></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-[#2A2A2A]/50 hover:bg-[#151515] transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 p